## Hosting (Android TV compatible)

| Mode | Description |
|------|-------------|
| **DuckDNS + Caddy + Let's Encrypt (DNS-01)** | Default recommended. Free dynamic DNS, automatic trusted HTTPS via Caddy DNS-01 challenge. No router port forwarding required — the service stays LAN-only. |
| **Tailscale Funnel** | No port forwarding needed. Public HTTPS via `*.ts.net`. |

See the full hosting guide: [README_HOST.md](https://github.com/${REPO}/blob/${TAG}/README_HOST.md)

---

## Install in Stremio

Once the add-on is running and your hostname resolves, open this URL on your Android TV or any Stremio client:

```
https://YOUR-HOSTNAME/manifest.json
```

